For me, it looks like an issue in the Kotlin compiler because if you inline code of this function by yourself it will work fine:
```
fun Foo.captitalize2() = when {
    bar != null -&gt; try {
        Result.success(bar.capitalize())
    } catch (e: Throwable) {
